    <item>
      <title>Paytm 股价因新一轮监管审查报告而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/paytm-shares-drop-after-report-on-fresh-regulatory-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，印度市场监管机构要求 Paytm 提供更多与首次公开募股相关的信息，这可能会加剧这家金融科技先驱的监管问题，此后 Paytm 股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/paytm-shares-drop-after-report-on-fresh-regulatory-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:53:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uber 因向美国传输数据被罚款 3.24 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/uber-hit-by-record-324-million-fine-for-data-transfers-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[优步科技公司 (Uber Technologies Inc.) 因向美国传输大量有关其司机的敏感数据而未能遵守欧洲保护标准，被荷兰隐私监管机构处以创纪录的 2.9 亿欧元（3.24 亿美元）罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/uber-hit-by-record-324-million-fine-for-data-transfers-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:05:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国违约企业启迪控股终止债务重组计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/chinese-defaulter-tus-holdings-may-delay-payment-under-debt-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国科技园区运营商启迪控股股份有限公司取消了其境外债务重组计划，称由于缺乏监管部门批准，该公司无法在周一的最后期限前向债权人偿还债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-26/chinese-defaulter-tus-holdings-may-delay-payment-under-debt-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 04:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
